---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <main class="container mx-auto px-6 py-32 flex flex-col gap-12">
    <section class="flex flex-col gap-6 max-w-2xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-medium">About Billy Bronco</h1>

      <p>
        Hi, I’m Billy Bronco — a software engineer based in Pomona, CA. I’m
        passionate about building scalable web applications and creating
        meaningful digital experiences.
      </p>

      <p>
        I’m currently studying Computer Science at Cal Poly Pomona, where I’m
        actively involved in the Software Engineering Association (SEA). I enjoy
        working on projects that combine design, performance, and usability.
      </p>

      <p>
        Outside of coding, I enjoy collaborating on hackathons, exploring new
        technologies, and helping other students grow in tech.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium">Skills</h2>
      <ul class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-black/70">
        <li>JavaScript / TypeScript</li>
        <li>Astro</li>
        <li>React</li>
        <li>Tailwind CSS</li>
        <li>Node.js</li>
        <li>Git & GitHub</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>